<br>
The guests stood as both entered the sacred area of Scynthia blessed specifically for them this night.<br>
<br>
They smiled and joined hands and awaited the upcomming events previous to their bonding for eternity. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> Sariah Scynthian Shamaness</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(4/14/01 4:02:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=115.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Undieing Love. . . </span><hr size=1> Sariah stepped forward and smiled announcing.<br>
